---

<section id="features" class="relative py-32 bg-surface-base overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Golden Thread Container -->
    <div
        class="absolute left-6 md:left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-[1px] bg-border-weak -translate-x-1/2 hidden md:block"
    >
        <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand to-transparent"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="sticky top-1/2 w-3 h-3 bg-brand rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(200,170,110,0.6)]"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <!-- Feature 1: Welcome Rooms -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-32 group">
            <div class="order-2 md:order-1 text-right md:pr-16 space-y-6">
                <div
                    class="inline-block px-3 py-1 border border-brand/30 rounded-full text-xs text-brand tracking-widest uppercase mb-2"
                >
                    El Portal
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-content-primary"
                >
                    Salas de Bienvenida
                </h3>
                <p
                    class="text-content-secondary font-light leading-relaxed text-lg"
                >
                    Olvídese de los correos perdidos. Envíe un <span
                        class="text-content-primary">Link Mágico</span
                    >. Su cliente entra a un entorno seguro, firma el contrato y
                    sube sus documentos. Sin apps, sin registros complejos.
                </p>
                <ul
                    class="text-sm text-content-muted space-y-2 inline-block text-right"
                >
                    <li class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2">
                        Firma Digital Simple <span class="text-brand">✓</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2">
                        Carga de Archivos Segura <span class="text-brand"
                            >✓</span
                        >
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="order-1 md:order-2 relative">
                <div
                    class="aspect-video bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-sm shadow-2xl p-2 transform group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-700"
                >
                    <!-- Mockup Content Placeholder -->
                    <div
                        class="w-full h-full bg-surface-base rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center border border-dashed border-border/50"
                    >
                        <span class="text-content-muted font-light"
                            >Interfaz del Cliente</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Decorative Glow -->
                <div
                    class="absolute -inset-4 bg-brand/5 blur-2xl -z-10 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"
                >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2: Brand Identity -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-32 group">
            <div class="order-1 relative md:pl-16">
                <div
                    class="aspect-video bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-sm shadow-2xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 transform group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-700"
                >
                    <!-- Logo Transformation Animation (CSS) -->
                    <div class="text-center space-y-2">
                        <div
                            class="text-xs text-content-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-4"
                        >
                            Su Marca Aquí
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="w-16 h-16 bg-content-primary rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 animate-pulse"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="h-4 w-32 bg-content-primary/20 rounded mx-auto"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute -inset-4 bg-brand/5 blur-2xl -z-10 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"
                >
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="order-2 text-left md:pl-16 space-y-6">
                <div
                    class="inline-block px-3 py-1 border border-brand/30 rounded-full text-xs text-brand tracking-widest uppercase mb-2"
                >
                    Identidad
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-content-primary"
                >
                    Su Marca es lo Primero
                </h3>
                <p
                    class="text-content-secondary font-light leading-relaxed text-lg"
                >
                    El portal lleva <span class="text-content-primary"
                        >su logo</span
                    > y nombre. Para el cliente, es <em>su</em> tecnología, no la
                    nuestra. Proyecte la autoridad de una firma global desde el primer
                    día.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3: Collaboration -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center group">
            <div class="order-2 md:order-1 text-right md:pr-16 space-y-6">
                <div
                    class="inline-block px-3 py-1 border border-brand/30 rounded-full text-xs text-brand tracking-widest uppercase mb-2"
                >
                    Control
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-content-primary"
                >
                    Colaboración Centralizada
                </h3>
                <p
                    class="text-content-secondary font-light leading-relaxed text-lg"
                >
                    Centralice el trabajo de sus asociados. Asigne expedientes,
                    controle permisos y supervise el avance de todo el bufete
                    desde un panel maestro.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="order-1 md:order-2 relative">
                <div
                    class="aspect-video bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-sm shadow-2xl p-4 flex items-center justify-center transform group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-700"
                >
                    <!-- Network Graphic Placeholder -->
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 w-full max-w-xs">
                        <div
                            class="h-24 bg-surface-base border border-border rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center"
                        >
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand/20"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="h-24 bg-surface-base border border-border rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center"
                        >
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand/20"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="col-span-2 h-12 bg-surface-highlight rounded-sm border border-brand/30 flex items-center justify-center"
                        >
                            <span class="text-xs text-brand tracking-widest"
                                >DASHBOARD CENTRAL</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute -inset-4 bg-brand/5 blur-2xl -z-10 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"
                >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
